OL,6,FMr Williamson, who has never been
OL,7,Fcharged with any criminal offences,
OL,8,Fwas sacked in 2015 for inappropriate
OL,9,Fbehaviour towards a female member of
OL,10,Fstaff. The report found the hospital
OL,11,Ftrust did not properly investigate
OL,12,Fallegations of bullying and unsafe
OL,13,Fcare and had it done so, further harm
OL,14,Fto patients could have been avoided.
OL,16,FEmily Bhogal was 12 when Mr Williamson
OL,17,Fcarried out surgery to treat her
OL,18,FScoliosis. She had two metal rods and
OL,19,F10 screws inserted into her back.
