OL,6,FDays after surgery she collapsed with
OL,7,Fa life threatening medical condition
OL,8,Fwhich the surgeon denied was related
OL,9,Fto the operation.
OL,11,FShe has since found out at least five
OL,12,Fof the screws were put in the wrong
OL,13,Fplace.
OL,15,FEmily said: "I just constantly feel as
OL,16,Fif my rods are being torn out of my
OL,17,Fback. It feels as if they are moving
OL,18,Fconstantly and it doesn't feel as if
OL,19,Fthey are in place. It doesn't feel as
OL,20,Fif they are where they are supposed to
OL,21,Fbe."
