OL,6,FThe mother of one said: "When I
OL,7,Finitially had the surgery my posture
OL,8,Fwas very straight. Now I can't sit
OL,9,Fback in a chair I am constantly leant
OL,10,Fforward.
OL,12,F"I have no flexibility in my spine
OL,13,Fwhatsoever so I struggle on a day to
OL,14,Fday basis getting up, getting dressed.
OL,16,F"Sometimes I can't get out of bed in
OL,17,Fthe morning due to this but it has
OL,18,Fgradually got worse since the surgery
OL,19,Fand I wasn't in this pain before the
OL,20,Fsurgery."
