OL,6,FEmily, who has had to give up her job
OL,7,Fas a teacher due to her health issues,
OL,8,Fadded: "The amount of reports and the
OL,9,Famount of issues that have come up
OL,10,Fwith this spinal surgeon- why wasn't
OL,11,Fthis looked at before?
OL,13,F"Why have patients not been listened
OL,14,Fto? Why have parents not been listened
OL,15,Fto? Lives have been lost and lives
OL,16,Fhave been damaged."
OL,18,FIn March, Emily received a letter
OL,19,Fsaying her treatment had been reviewed
OL,20,Fas part of an investigation by the
OL,21,FRoyal Manchester Children's Hospital.
